Arlene Dahl https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arlene_Dahl 0 Arlene Carol Dahl (born August 11, 1925) is an American actress and former Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer contract star, who achieved notability during the 1950s. She has three children, the eldest of whom is actor Lorenzo Lamas. She is one of the last surviving stars from the Golden Age of Hollywood.
